title: "CRediT Generator"
abstract: >-
  A client-side web app and TypeScript library for drafting CRediT (Contributor Roles Taxonomy) contribution statements for scholarly publications, with a contribution heatmap and JATS4R XML, CSV, JSON, and Markdown exports for journal submission systems.
